{
  "texts": [
    "Eventually, it will hit the file size limit for a file (100 MiB) [65].",
    "Having a back-up plan for data sharing when this happens and a process for navigating the transition in a transparent way without gaps in access to the data ensures continual functionality.",
    "Teams may do this by changing reference URLs to the data and ensuring that code further on in the pipeline references the most up-to-date storage location.",
    "Often, as changes are being made, there should be a working prototype available in the meantime.",
    "However, there may be cases where service should be discontinued until changes are officially made."
  ]
}